frase2: We make the world a cleaner place

about-us.p: Chilean company founded in 2018 by 3 Electrical Engineers of the University of Chile. We are dedicated to developing renewable generation projects and connection studies to high and medium voltage power grids. We are committed to excellence and decarbonization of the energy matrix.
